726877f-b.text:
Hollis Avenue, west side, south of Jamaica Avenue, showing the old Hollis District Schoolhouse No. 2, from 1860 to 1890. Henry Miller's bicycle repair shop was here in the 1920's
and early '30's.

Views 1,2:  Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
View 1: 1923
View 2: 1925

View 3: P. L. Sperr
March 25, 1932
